    HOW DOES IT WORK?

    CUSTOMILY'S ADMIN

    Customily's Admin allows you to transform your static products into customizable ones. Manage products, set personalization areas and parameters, define output methods for printing and engraving, upload artworks, fonts, colors, pictures, masks and other settings.

    WOOCOMMERCE'S  ADMIN

    Once Customily is installed, our software pulls the products along with their details from your WooCommerce store, and links them with Customily's Admin .

    You can define which products from your store can or cannot be customized, add your different personalization options (such as text input, picture upload, color selection, etc.) directly from your WooCommerce Admin panel.

    Once you save all the settings, the dynamic personalization will automatically appear on your product page.

    Instead of a static and boring product picture, customers will see a real dynamic preview of your product, which they will use to design within the specified personalization parameters.

    Customily's online product designer is fully responsive, producing high quality previews for web and mobile.
